general.name: photoFirst
general.short: migrated from old datamodel - needs update
general.description: Match of objects in a field of an SDSS imaging catalog to the FIRST radio survey catalog (2008 version). These matches are to any objects which are RUN_PRIMARY according to the local resolve (see resolve documentation ). Results are reported for all objects, and "first_skyrms" reports the noise level of FIRST at each location.

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
